data.description: This quaint home in Mint Hill has an amazing prize, a huge yard, and so much potential. In the heart of Lawyers Station on a cul-de-sac, this home offers tons of trees and privacy and room to breathe. The first floor offers a private study, a large homey great room with fireplace, and an open kitchen. Upstairs are three bedrooms including the primary bedroom and en suite. There is an awesome deck at the back of the home that is perfect for entertaining and overlooks the yard. Don't miss this home!
